title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Jun 25 2022

description:
U.S. Navy training video on pronoun usage. Megan Rapinoe says your daughter's sports career doesn't matter because transgenders need your support. Senator Marsha Blackburn wishes C&B a happy anniversary. More on Megan Rapinoe's outrageous comments on transgenders in sports. Michael Berry wishes C&B a happy anniversary. Hilarious Trump pledges to never, ever ride a bicycle after Biden fall.
